<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Authentication Not Configured - Standup Bot</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 40 40' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Crect width='40' height='40' rx='10' fill='%23667eea'/%3E%3Cpath d='M12 28V16L20 12L28 16V28L20 32L12 28Z' stroke='white' stroke-width='2' fill='none'/%3E%3Ccircle cx='20' cy='20' r='4' fill='white'/%3E%3Cpath d='M20 8V12M20 28V32M8 20H12M28 20H32' stroke='white' stroke-width='2' stroke-linecap='round'/%3E%3C/svg%3E">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 1rem;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            max-width: 550px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        .icon { 
            font-size: 4rem; 
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            display: block;
        }
        
        h1 { 
            color: #f59e0b; 
            margin-bottom: 1rem; 
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        
        p { 
            color: #64748b; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        
        code {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Consolas', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #667eea;
        }
        
        .warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1), rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05));
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .warning p {
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
            color: #78350f;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .warning p:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea, #764ba2);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.5);
        }
        
        .hint {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .hint strong {
            color: #64748b;
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .container {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .warning {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <span class="icon">⚠️</span>
        <h1>Authentication Not Configured</h1>
        <p>Clerk authentication is not set up. The dashboards are currently <strong>publicly accessible</strong> without authentication.</p>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <p>To enable authentication, add these to your .env file:</p>
            <p><code>CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_...</code></p>
            <p><code>CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_...</code></p>
        </div>
        
        <p class="hint">
            For detailed setup instructions, see <strong>AUTHENTICATION_SETUP.md</strong>
        </p>
        
        <a href="/" class="btn">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
